{"type": "article", "id": 23009, "title": "这些可移动的小木屋比房车便宜，而且更像个家", "description": "它拥有简洁的外观，实用的功能和可承受的价格。\r\n", "date": "2016-02-29T16:33:58Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 19098, "name": "木屋"}, {"id": 1225, "name": "美国"}, {"id": 24132, "name": "Traveler"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 19, "praise_count": 509, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702154927ZsE8QqoNP4HdOT9u.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>Traveler 是美国一家生产可移动小木屋的品牌，就是那种挂在汽车后面、自己带有轮子、可以被运输到各个地方的小房子。</p>\n<p> <a href=\"http://www.escapetraveler.net/#!models/cfvg\">Traveler 已推出了 3 款类似小屋</a>，它的外形像一个盒子，只有大概 20 平米的室内面积，却容纳了起居室、床、厨房、浴室等一个“家”的所有要素。他们生产的木屋已经获得了 RVIA (Recreational Vehicle Industry Association，美国房车工业协会)的证明，意味着它可以实现标准化生产和出售。</p>\n<p>第一代 Traveler 于 2015 年推出，有 269 平方英尺（约 24 平方米），是长条形的。门在中间的位置，一头放着可作为床的沙发，配有电视机，另一头连着一个完整的卫生间。而最大的玻璃窗前放上了一张小桌，室内所有家具都用浅色的木头定制，相互配合，也非常温馨。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154905c5oIbJWgPlmkMLrY.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154907fnzxRGASIeLD16lY.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154908UY0GRKpgEsc6bwCT.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">屋子的两头含有 loft 夹层，分别放上一张大床，因而一共有 3 张床，可以容纳 6 个人，房间和家具一共售价 65400 美元。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154910B1xWbi3IouF2NCLv.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">对着门的墙面是一排橱柜，功能非常齐全</div></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021549110soNvYtSfpGrQOTg.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">两边 loft 床铺</div></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021549120PAJmy9bS8NeIQkg.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">高低床</div></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154914wPcoS2bvpyqAQYn3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.10859729\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154914przIJKatLV4UOMnm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.041841\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\n<p class=\"\">在标准款 Traveler 之外，他们推出了 Traveler XL，模式大同小异，但面积扩大到 344 平方英尺（约 32 平方米），可以放上一个单独的沙发，最多能容纳 8 个人，售价 72800 美元 。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021549150OY4NgjmrLRfPbuT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154915Dhc1tpLY7ETPuwg2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021549169LJfxCDc2qrROKdl.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154917dfEuJr7h3BH6Rs4D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154918Tae5ZkHXNVEDIYiC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50098232\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154919y3WowHRbFdK251zf.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154920b47NPxpusT1ef3dg.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154921VxoWqSR23cX5eYlO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.94611529\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>最新推出的<a href=\"http://www.escapevista.com\"> vista </a>倒是一个小型的木屋，有 160 平方英尺的室内面积（不到 15 平方米），用松木和耐候钢搭建，是为了适应更极端的天气而设计。房间的布局与前面两者类似，但没有 loft 的设计，因而只能容纳 2 个人。</p>\n<p class=\"\">在功能上，他们增加了许多储物空间，让这个木屋更居家。玻璃窗几乎环绕了小屋的四周，仿佛身处于自然之中，可以更好地欣赏风景。这个木屋售价 39900 美元。<a href=\"http://www.escapetraveler.net/#!models/cfvg\">如果有兴趣可以点击这里查看。</a></p>\n<p>          </p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154921TAsP1DIj39f4QKHw.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154922PwG9qRsoJkrz6ASB.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021549226QgGtXJ9nHuRI8kd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154923j38soBa0O1dQTmiX.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154923rgj8bLGDWowftCO4.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154925y7Aq2TDwfeGg3V80.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75186567\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154925b4rmwvjuWftqCSgo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61002445\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154926RQxznqDYCfMPVes1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52444988\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021549265kBdJ2nq6QWgLfcb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69437653\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021549272efLuRHoJTZ8biUj.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59779951\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">图片来自 <a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/architecture/escape-vista-corten-steel-mobile-cabin-escape-homes-02-26-2016/\">designboom</a>、<a href=\"http://www.escapevista.com\">escapevista</a></p>\n\n"}